<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mstḥq ạlsjwd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mstḥq ạlsjwd .. ạlḥml ạlly ạ̹ndbḥ
 dạ ṣlybk fyh sẖfạnạ .. lynạ ḥryẗ wfrḥ)2
 wbqlwbnạ nyjy lyk .. wbsjwdnạ bnʿlyk
 dạ ạldẖnwb ʿndk mgẖfwrẗ .. wkl ḥml ynṭrḥ
 ạlqrạr- (yạlly dfʿt tmn kẖṭạyạnạ .. yạlly btʿzy kl ḥzạny̱
 yạlly ạ̹nt kạsẖf ạ̹yh jwạnạ .. sjwdnạ lyk yạ yswʿ)2
 sjwdnạ lyk yạ yswʿ
 2- (nyjy lyk zy mạ ạḥnạ .. jwh qlbk mḥfwryn
 rgẖm kl ḍʿf fynạ .. fy ṣlybk mqbwlyn)2
 ạlbʿyd ạ̹nt tlạqyh .. sẖwfnạ ḥbk qd ạ̹yh
 rạḥ ndws ʿly̱ ạlkẖṭạyạ .. wbạlmbạhj nsthyn</lyrics>
<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
